<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1422510-what-is-the-meaning-of-the-title-the">What is the meaning of the title, &#39;The Sunne in Splendour&#39;?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1422510'><a id="like_count_community_question_1422510" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1422510?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F119829.The_Sunne_in_Splendour">like</a></span>

</li>
