</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/105194994-pauline-calkin"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/105194994-pauline-calkin">Pauline Calkin</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is a symbol of the House of York after Edward (to become King Edward IV) won a crucial victory at the battle of Mortimer’s Cross. Before the battle<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is a symbol of the House of York after Edward (to become King Edward IV) won a crucial victory at the battle of Mortimer’s Cross. Before the battle, three suns appeared in the sky, the result of a phenomenon known as a parahelion.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
